2/15/26
does anyone keep blogs anymore? one time i met a guy traveling who kept a blog for his friends back home. he would post every two weeks with details from a backpacking trip. he said he made the site and wrote his posts. we got closer and turns out he actually did build the website, but use ai to write the blog posts. ?? like why keep a blog if u don't like to write and it doesn't mean anything to you. it should be the other way round, use ai to make the site than write all the posts urself.
